Use the standard library
This is how to split_words of txt:
   Remember that words is []
   Remember that word is []
   Remember that i is 0

   Do this txt's length times:
      Remember that ch is item i in txt
      When ch is 32, then:
         When word's length is more than 0, then:
            Add words to word
            Remember that word is []
         End when
      But, if not:
         When ch is 44, then:
            When word's length is more than 0, then:
               Add words to word
               Remember that word is []
            End when
         But, if not:
            Add word to ch
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   When word's length is more than 0, then:
      Add words to word
   End when

   The answer is words
Now you know